head_commit.message:
Add signal functionalities (#38)

* feat: add basic signal support

* feat(signal): add test_sigkill_stop

* style: format

* feat(signal): add basic sigtimedwait & sigsuspend

* fix: clone

adapt to arceos change

* feat(clone): add settls

fix(signal): sigtimedwait

* feat(signal): add tkill & tgkill

* feat(signal): add sigaltstack

* feat(signal): add exit signal

* feat(clone): add SIGHAND

* feat: add rt_sigqueueinfo

* doc: add comments for thread functions

* refactor: sys_kill

* refactor: get_thread_checked -> find_thread_in_group

* fix(signal): add thorough check in sigqueueinfo

* style: remove unnecessary convert

* refactor: clone argument name

---------
